-*- texinfo -*-
@deftypefn {Loadable Function} {@var{val} =} automatic_replot ()
@deftypefnx {Loadable Function} {@var{old_val} =} automatic_replot (@var{new_val})
Query or set the current automatic replot state.  Although it is fairly
inefficient, especially for large plots, automatic replotting is enabled
by default for compatibility with Matlab.
@end deftypefn
